snippet.title: Don't open the doors!
snippet.description:
The game IS OUT NOW ON STEAM!
http://store.steampowered.com//app/533950

=============================

"Don't open the doors!" is a claymotion action adventure in an odd world of talking pumpkins, blue trees and stuff like that.

Help to the game on indiegogo: http://igg.me/at/doors/
